name: Wet n Wild Always Naked Palette Always Nude 1114216
reviews: First off, the first one I ordered arrived shattered.  About half of the shadows were completely gone.  I told Amazon and I was sent a new one immediately without charge.  The second arrived well packaged and completely safe.  If it arrives broken, just tell them.That being said, this is an AWESOME palette.  My main gripe with most 'neutral' palettes is that they are not actually neutral.  They are usually more warm toned and not true taupe type shades.  This is NOT  that palette.  Every shade has that true neutral undertone making it go great with everything.  The pigments are long lasting and blend like a high end palette.  There is some fall out, but I get the same fall out in ND palettes, so it definitely is not a deal breaker.  I have some expensive palettes and this is at the top of my list of daily wear.  I still reach for the others, but only to add pops of color if I want it with this palette as my base colors.  The best part is it is so affordable that I can repurchase it when I hit pan on one or two colors without feeling like I just wasted so much money or....hunting down ten different individual shades to find one JUST like my favorite in a palette that is way too expensive to repurchase just for one color.  I feel like I hit gold with this one.  Oh, and Tati brought me to it.
date.of.review: Reviewed in the United States on 14 April 2023
